com.google.common.css.compiler.passes

Class ChunkCompactPrinter<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.common.css.compiler.passes.UniformVisitor
      • com.google.common.css.compiler.passes.CodePrinter
        • com.google.common.css.compiler.passes.CompactPrinter
          • com.google.common.css.compiler.passes.ChunkCompactPrinter<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of chunk id objects set on CssSelectorNode instances
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    AtRuleHandler, CssCompilerPass, CssTreeVisitor
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    TemplateCompactPrinter

    public class ChunkCompactPrinter<T>
extends CompactPrinter
    Compact-printer for CssTree instances that only outputs rulesets which include a selector belonging to one chunk. This printer does not support code moving between chunks and ouputs the same ruleset for as many chunks as this ruleset belongs to.

    This pass can only be used if MapChunkAwareNodesToChunk pass has been run before. Otherwise this pass won't work.

    Author:
    dgajda@google.com (Damian Gajda)
